{"tid":504526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母親借錢助兒子在歌壇發展 張如城母子遭追債逾130萬元","createTime":"2017-12-20T06:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T06:42:56.000Z","uid":24160,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aacf44af4fd1f266debae32f8d5ff8c8daaffd96","tid":504526,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"有「亞洲神童」、被網民戲稱為「章如城」的獨立歌手張如城(29歲)，遭母親的男性好友入稟高院，指張母為幫助張如城在歌壇發展，於2016至2017年間向他借貸共16.5萬港幣及120萬人民幣，當時張如城及另外3人曾承諾若張母未能還款，他們會代為還債，但4人最終沒有兌現承諾，男友人現向張如城及其母等共5人索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告何海濤控告張如城、張母歐景嵐、張如龍、張如珠及張如鳳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171220/large/1513748721_92c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171220%2Flarge%2F1513748721_92c6.jpg&h=05d33627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張如城(中)去年有新歌推出(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171220/57605004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57605004&d=Xg0MilhLFswsUtwzR4mAVJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=38522297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57605004&h=ad6f47f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171220/57605004</a>"},{"pid":"a3f19522afbf88a18b6a0e22321e5076585558d0","tid":504526,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"成家都on99.."},{"pid":"98adee2a894e5164f7438ba69e06470d924f7362","tid":504526,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"賣佢老母落火坑啦"},{"pid":"4b491776f770a8388b56c157a5d85e170c71e0f7","tid":504526,"uid":16250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk